title: EasyUEFI WinToUSB Enterprise v3.1
description:
EasyUEFI WinToUSB Enterprise v3.1

WinToUSB (also called Windows To USB) is the best free Windows To Go Creator that allows you to install and run Windows operating system on an external hard drive or USB flash drive, using an ISO/WIM/ESD/SWM/VHD/VHDX image file or CD/DVD drive as the source of installation, or you can clone current Windows OS installation (Windows 7 or later) to a USB drive as a Windows To Go Workspace. WinToUSB also supports creating a Windows installation USB flash drive from a Windows 10/8.1/8/7/Vista/2008/2012/2016 installation ISO file, so you can install Windows from the USB flash drive easily. Oh, WinToUSB also supports creating a bootable Windows PE USB drive, it can help you transfer the contents of Windows PE to a USB drive and make the USB drive bootable.

Create Windows To Go Workspace from an ISO/WIM/ESD/SWM/VHD File or a CD/DVD Drive
Create Windows To Go Workspace from an Encrypted ESD or VHDX File
Create Windows To Go Workspace on a Non-Certified Windows To Go USB Drive
Create VHD-based Windows To Go Workspace
Create VHDX-based Windows To Go Workspace
Support for Non-Enterprise Edition of Windows 10/8.1/8/7
Support for Enterprise Edition of Windows 10/8.1/8/7
Other Advanced Features
Clone speed - Faster
No upgrade prompts
Business usagequestion
Priority technical support - High
License agreement - Enterprise License
Number of computers allowed to install - Unlimited PCs

Official Site: http://www.easyuefi.com/wintousb/index.html
